    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new ride? I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's looking for a great new home! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for all my daily commutes. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved over the years. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019ll make its next owner very happy! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show you around the car!",
