      "timestep_posted": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This example is mechanically sound, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory M-variable differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a structural subframe inspection to ensure chassis rigidity. The suspension maintains its factory-spec geometry, offering the precise turn-in and communicative feedback characteristic of the chassis. While it shows honest patina from spirited use, the throttle response remains sharp and the power delivery linear. A mechanically honest specimen for the purist driver.",
